{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he liked to go actually to the laundry, for we were inside of the laundry, he didn't have to pay any attention to anything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So he sat there and smoked a pipe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when it came to the lunch break, so we have been sitting in a kind of a half circle, and in front or me there are two SS men who are eating salami and bread and drinking beer to it.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had their soup or something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Romejko, would start being talkative, and he would say, so what can you-- what can you do, you bums?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am translating from German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Using the word schlawiner, it's-- means 'bums.' Nothing too bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For an SS man, not too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were so trained that, I remember we have been eight at that point, and in unison-- we trained it-- in unison we said to him, Nix, Herr Oberscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing, Herr Oberscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "O-B-E-R-S-C-H-A-R-F-U with an-H-R-E-R.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nix, Herr Obserscharfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, eh, I?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He call Lesen-- Lesen, L-E-S-E-N.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The N he didn't pronounce.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Schreiben, S-C-H-R-E-I-B-E-N he didn't pronounce.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can even ride the horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What can-- what can you do, your bums?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing, Herr Obescharffhrer.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then he took another bite and he looked at us, kind of a glorious look, and he would say, I can also ride a bike, you bums.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I am an artist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am an artist of thousand arts, a thousand kunstler, an artist of thousand arts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as he made the break, so we gave him a hand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we put him into  a situation that he didn't know really how to react.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so it happened that he never hit, never beat anyone of my commando.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had him tamed.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
